{"tid":1899220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔要食魚蛋 黑警陷家產","createTime":"2020-02-26T12:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T12:58:44.000Z","uid":239389,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"65b9cbf061c4e410a5dfe8bd718fb3454cbb9ed1","tid":1899220,"uid":239389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:51:55.000Z","msg":"黃子華呢段 相信很多人都有睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-30Q5JKHqZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-30Q5JKHqZA&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=35017bb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-30Q5JKHqZA</a><br />\n<br />\n喂大佬呀 依家好明顯林鄭政府叫個死人波出黎做緊同一樣野<br />\n拿 你班仆街辛苦啦 依家我地呢就一人派一萬<br />\n你地可唔可以收皮呀<br />\n咁我同時又會比我班狗仔一筆錢去入6架車<br />\n遲下你地又出黎呢就可以一野車鳩死你地班仆街<br />\n袋住呢一萬先好唔好呀 乖乖地 我餵你地就好好地食啦<br />\n<br />\n依家我屌你老母呀<br />\n我唔係要你傷害完個社會 整死左香港人之後<br />\n每人派一萬叫我地收皮呀 點撚袋得落呀<br />\n依家唔撚想要你粒魚蛋 同我拎走去<br />\n唔係要你補償咩比我地呢班香港人<br />\n我係要你拎撚柒走你比班狗既魚蛋呀<br />\n錢我地可以照收 帛金又好 慰問金又好 補償又好<br />\n你想點叫果一萬都可以 但我地絕對唔認同<br />\n你派埋俾班死黑警 屌你老母同我拎撚走去呀<br />\n全部人同我大聲叫一次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔要食魚蛋 黑警陷家產</span></span>"},{"pid":"c2c1cabdd2d5f5fb0d4cf0a81074caafc8dc6e4b","tid":1899220,"uid":239389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:55:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔要食魚蛋 黑警陷家產</span></span>"},{"pid":"924034f038733d7f839fc2a0a0b6e52846dab7c7","tid":1899220,"uid":239389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c2c1cabdd2d5f5fb0d4cf0a81074caafc8dc6e4b","tid":1899220,"uid":239389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:55:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔要食魚蛋 黑警陷家產</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔要食魚蛋 黑警陷家產</span></span>"},{"pid":"ffdaec